33
00:02:22,410 --> 00:02:25,210
Someone who'll never bother to take them up.

34
00:02:25,210 --> 00:02:27,630
Who asked you to do anything?

35
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:29,970
Why are you even here?

36
00:02:29,970 --> 00:02:38,150
