66
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:05,531
Yeah. We don't.

67
00:05:05,531 --> 00:05:10,471
We've got enough problems without you lot starting a bloody riot!

68
00:05:10,471 --> 00:05:15,260
Mind your tongue! They're your elders!
-Well they better behave like it!

69
00:05:15,260 --> 00:05:20,907
All I see is a bunch of filthy rabble-rousers, all wrapped up in their blasted selves!

70
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:29,620
