81
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:39,250
Just... Go. Right now.

82
00:06:39,250 --> 00:06:45,004
Go back where you've come from. Go to Britain, America, or Timbuc-blasted-too!

83
00:06:45,004 --> 00:06:50,925
